		<element name="Montral" type="Racial Trait" source="GM Binder SW5E" id="ID_GMBINDER_SW5E_RACIAL_TRAIT_TOGRUTA_MONTRAL">
			<description>
				<p>Togrutan's horns on their heads give them echolocation up to 60ft unless they are deafened or there is a significant amount of background noise, such as in cities or near loud vehicles or waterfalls.</p>
			</description>
			<sheet>
				<description>
